  Question: ' Bitcoin surges 14% today!'
  Desc: Bitcoin jumped 14% after ETF approval news.Social media is filled with people
    claiming huge profits.
  Lesson: Large price moves often pause or pull back.Don't buy simply because everyone
    else is buying.
  cmt1: Going to $100k!
  cmt2: This is just beginning!
  cmt3: Dont miss out!
  CorrectOption: 1
  CorrectWhatHappenDec: Bitcoin pulled back 8% after the initial rally as many traders
    took profits. Waiting for confirmation helped you avoid buying near the top.
  CorrectLesson: Bitcoin pulled back 8% after the initial rally as many traders took
    profits. Waiting for confirmation helped you avoid buying near the top.
  WrongWhatHappenDec: You reacted to the excitement and entered during a rapid price
    surge. Soon after, the market pulled back and your position lost value.
  WrongLesson: Don't chase prices just because everyone else is buying.
